Title: Forecast Linear AugmentedProjection (FLAP): A Free Lunch to Reduce Forecast Error Variance
Author-Name: Yangzhuoran Fin Yang 
Author-X-Name-First: Yangzhuoran
Author-X-Name-Last: Yang
